<pc>”</pc>紹興<measure quantity="3" unit="years">
<num value="3">三</num>年</measure>
<pc>，</pc>提舉製造軍器所言<pc>：</pc>
<pc>“</pc>
<quote>以<num value="70">七十</num>工造全裝甲<num value="1">一</num>
<pc>。</pc>又長齊頭甲每<num value="1">一</num>甲用工<num value="41">百四十一</num>
<pc>，</pc>短齊頭甲用工<num value="74">七十四</num>
<pc>。</pc>乞以本所全裝甲為定式<pc>。</pc>
